# Maintainer-only paths excluded from `git archive` (the adopter distribution).
# Affects ONLY git archive / scripts/adopter-export.sh — never the kit's own tree or CI.
# Link-safety: no KEPT doc has a `](path)` markdown link to any entry (S3 spec §4.1). Links
# BETWEEN export-ignored entries (ignored→ignored) are fine — both ends are pruned together;
# adopter-export-wired.sh enforces this by excluding the IGN set from its kept-doc link scan.
docs/ROADMAP-KIT.md                 export-ignore
.github/workflows/drift-watch.yml   export-ignore
.github/workflows/golden-path.yml   export-ignore
docs/superpowers/                   export-ignore
.superpowers/                       export-ignore
.github/CODEOWNERS                                                export-ignore
docs/architecture/                  export-ignore
docs/governance/meta-control-log.md                              export-ignore
docs/governance/.meta-control-last                              export-ignore
